Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脸上粘着什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑠川同学泡的红茶果然很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小爸爸就在这方面教了我很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶叶也是爸爸特地从英国带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是正统啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都能喝到这么好喝的红茶  太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也很香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上为两位准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank  you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们马上开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围绕永不凋零的樱花发生过的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天去向老师们打听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向老师们打听？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花上一次凋零是20多年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有很多老师知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有可能找到一些线索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去图书室调查一下过去的文献好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  那明天就要分头行动了
