Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.94,Newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs17\fad(300,0)}发现现代的忍者！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.94,Newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs17\fad(300,0)}不同的藏身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.94,Newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs17\fad(300,0)}据传是学园里的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.94,Newspaper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs17\fad(300,0)}新的忍者类型！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非官方新闻！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么混在这里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  非官方新闻这么久以前就有了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  非官方新闻可是有着悠久的历史呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  事件和事故竟然这么频繁地发生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  不要那么干脆地无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs17\an8}（神秘少女  在学校出现！？）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神秘少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该都三十多岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我非得应你的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图书室内请保持安静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说  我和你之间可是争夺杉并大人的对手关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你会对我抱有敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你有在听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太近了  脸太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦  都怪你不听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也算是个外表可爱的女孩子  要多注意一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可爱什么的  你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你色诱我也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神秘少女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在樱花凋零之前  有见到那样的少女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听是听说过  但从没见过那样的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是听说过只要对樱花许愿就能实现任何愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那只是个传说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也只是个传说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里啊  歌丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可担心你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬到树上不敢下来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  歌丸  你在搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  真是只奇怪的…猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸就是歌丸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸  让朋友担心可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  刚刚的声音不是樱发出来的  是歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这种东西能填饱肚子么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸也想吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:14:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫也吃豆沙包的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  居然喜欢日式点心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱果然很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  感觉有点古朴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不苦  很甜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客气客气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子也填饱了  我们去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真败给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是刀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:16:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是密探  歌丸是恶代官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么设定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂堂正正决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了也没人捡尸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧  歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来玩抓人游戏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可擅长抓人游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我什么时候睡着的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你玩了很久  然后累得睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷不冷  差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  再看一会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳也下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定还会见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见啦  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:20:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走咯  歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱  真是个奇怪的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸  那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.64,0:23:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我  歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆沙包真是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能和哥哥一起玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐看起来好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  希望永远停留的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
